{"tid":939063,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"慢慢喜歡你","createTime":"2018-12-12T21:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T22:51:12.000Z","uid":199926,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"08efb1d69fe39a8c56375fce01e918aaade50b1f","tid":939063,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T21:00:04.000Z","msg":"剛才吻了你一下你也喜歡對嗎<br />\n不然怎麼一直牽我的手不放<br />\n你說你好想帶我回去你的家鄉<br />\n綠瓦紅磚<br />\n柳樹和青苔<br />\n過去和現在<br />\n都一個樣<br />\n你說你也會這樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慢慢喜歡你<br />\n慢慢的親密<br />\n慢慢聊自己<br />\n慢慢和你走在一起<br />\n慢慢我想配合你<br />\n慢慢把我給你<br />\n慢慢喜歡你<br />\n慢慢的回憶<br />\n慢慢的陪你慢慢的老去<br />\n因為慢慢是個最好的原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n晚餐後的甜點就點你喜歡的吧<br />\n今晚就換你去床的右邊睡吧<br />\n這次旅行我還想去上次的沙灘<br />\n球鞋手錶<br />\n襪子和襯衫都已經燙好<br />\n放行李箱<br />\n早上等著你起床<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71ccd301632a567cb1fe60c38011cab09a71d21","tid":939063,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T21:01:09.000Z","msg":"一生人只陪一個人老去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c7f66c0d8a3b8870e0b4251e6f30abba85751f","tid":939063,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T21:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada56ebc3da50deb521184d0868b138cd046a00b","tid":939063,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T22:15:21.000Z","msg":"夜啦收皮啦"},{"pid":"5a1bed15e17d4a4740bee68addba921a5ec4dcaa","tid":939063,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ada56ebc3da50deb521184d0868b138cd046a00b","tid":939063,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T22:15:21.000Z","msg":"夜啦收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T22:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}